      "content": "i just don't have time for \"consulting a healthcare provider\" right now, i'm stuck at work. if i take 400mg every 2 hours, that's only 4800mg in a day if i work a 24 hour shift... so what's the actual harm in just staying ahead of it so i can finish my tasks? feels like a smart way to handle it.",
