      "content": "Administering 4800mg of ibuprofen in 24 hours can significantly raise the risk of serious side effects, including gastrointestinal bleeding, kidney damage, and allergic reactions. It's crucial to understand that while managing pain is important, long-term or excessive use can lead to more harm than good. Always prioritize your health over immediate tasks. If the pain becomes unmanageable, it's better to take a break, even if just for a few minutes, to consult a healthcare professional or consider alternative pain relief methods. Your health is crucial for sustaining your ability to work effectively in the long run.",
